name: Yellow Primula
description:
Card features bright yellow primulas. This has proved very popular and is nice and bright in the cold dark days of winter. Like all By HalveZ cards the image is printed over the front and back of the card roughly divided in half by the card spine.

All our cards are blank for your own message and are commercially printed on high quality semi gloss board using a lithographic process.

categories.name: A6 cellophane wrapped card with envelope. All images taken by our inhouse photographer.
